### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### ============================================
### PAYMENTS ENDPOINTS (Stripe)
### ============================================

### Create Stripe checkout session
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/create-checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "PRO"
}

### Get current user subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Stripe Webhook (Note: Requires Stripe CLI for local testing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
stripe-signature: your-stripe-signature-here

{
  "type": "checkout.session.completed",
  "data": {
    "object": {
      "id": "cs_test_xxx",
      "metadata": {
        "userId": "user-uuid-here"
      },
      "subscription": "sub_test_xxx"
    }
  }
}


